	  </para></listitem></varlistentry><varlistentry><term>
	  <code>nx, ny</code>
	  (<samp>PLINT</samp>, input)
	</term><listitem><para>
	    Physical dimensions of the arrays
	    <samp><code>u</code></samp> and
