Only retained for backward compatibility. Use the function <code>plscol0</code> (<pxref node="&#10;      plscol0;  Set a given color from color map0 by 8&#10;bit RGB value&#10;    " file=""/>)
instead.
    </para><varlist><varlistentry><term>
